Home-Desc-Local: A new journey begins. We are Saturn, a passionate robotics team starting our first season in the FIRST Tech Challenge. And Have The Best Cookies!
About-p1-Local: Saturn is a newly formed FIRST Tech Challenge team based in Albayda, Libya. This is our inaugural season, and we're excited to embark on this incredible journey of innovation, teamwork, and technological exploration.
About-p2-Local: Our mission is to inspire young minds through hands-on STEM education, fostering creativity, problem-solving skills, and collaboration. We believe that robotics is not just about building machines, but about building character, confidence, and community.
About-Boxes-Desc-b1-Local: We push boundaries and think outside the box
About-Boxes-Desc-b2-Local: Together we achieve more than individually
About-Boxes-Desc-b3-Local: We strive for the highest standards in everything
